Package: spEnviroDistr
Title: Spatial Environmental Data Distribution Tools
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Guillermo", "Fuentes-Jaque", , "g.fuentes@renare.uchile.cl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7864-4899"))
Description: This package provides tools for handling, analyzing, and visualizing spatial environmental data. It includes datasets and functions specifically tailored for geostatistical analysis and environmental modeling. The package offers the 'meuse' and 'meuse.grid' datasets, which are well-known examples for demonstrating spatial data analysis techniques.
